content: It's possible that we may see some familiar faces from the Star Wars universe in the High Republic era, as the timeline is still part of the overall Star Wars canon. However, the focus of this new era is on introducing new characters and storylines, so it may not rely heavily on callbacks or Easter eggs. That being said, the creators of the High Republic have mentioned that there may be some connections to the wider Star Wars universe, so there could be some surprises in store for fans.
